      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANOTHER ARTIST (2) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten 1.75 lengths, (16.07) at this track. Must come into calculations. HEY MAC (4) lines up chasing another win after scoring over 388m at Gosford in 22.20, set up by a fast early sectional. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. HARADA'S LASS (1) hit the ground running and on speed early but faded out of it to finish fourth (16.30) at this track over 272m. The form out of her last race has been franked. Should be about the money. MY WEE LASS (5) warrants respect with the drop in trip.",
